# TripPoint monorepo

TECH STACK:
- apps/mobile: React Native (Expo, TypeScript) + Supabase Auth/Client
- apps/api: Python FastAPI worker (Places/mock sync, route math, cache)
- Data: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage + RLS)

ARCHITECTURE (see docs/ARCHITECTURE.md):
- Supabase = source of truth + auth + POI read
- Python = sync-places / Places / marşrut riyaziyyatı / keş (writes via service role)
- Expo = UI only for those concerns; does not hold SERVICE_ROLE or Places keys

POI RULES:
- region ids lowercase: quba, qusar, seki, lerik, qabala
- upsert on place_id
- status for synced places: approved
- map coords: lat / lng

ƏSAS QAYDALAR:
- Auth/Supabase auth axınına toxunma (ayrı task olmadan)
- Mobile Supabase client: apps/mobile/lib/supabase.ts
- API secrets yalnız apps/api/.env
- Hər Supabase/API sorğusunda xətaları handle et
- Pul vahidi: AZN

QOVLUQ:
- apps/mobile/app → ekranlar
- apps/mobile/components → UI
- apps/mobile/lib → helpers + supabase
- apps/api → FastAPI (modular):
  - main.py / start.py = thin entry only
  - app/factory.py, config.py, db.py
  - app/routers/ = HTTP endpoints
  - app/services/ = sync/fetch/clean logic
  - app/constants/, app/data/ = maps & fixtures
  - Yeni kodu main.py-yə yığma; ehtiyac olsa yeni modul aç
